name: HAPPINESS
description:
I spent hours searching inside myself for something to offer to make the raven stay by my side ¿what do I have to give? I found stories to tell him, tears to quench his thirst and happiness to feed him, now he is here quietly on my lap, now he needs me and I need him !I am so happy! Loneliness shouldn't exist because it's a darkness from which it's difficult to get out
